@page "/badge"

<ElliciumText TextStyle="TextStyle.H2" TagName="TagName.H1" class="rz-pt-8">
    Badge
</ElliciumText>
<ElliciumText TextStyle="TextStyle.Subtitle1" TagName="TagName.P" class="rz-mb-8">
    The Ellicium Blazor <strong>Badge</strong> component is a small graphic that displays important information, like a count or label, within a user interface. It's commonly used to draw attention to something or provide visual feedback to the user.
</ElliciumText>
<ElliciumExample ComponentName="Badge" Example="BadgeUsage">
    <BadgeUsage />
</ElliciumExample>

<ElliciumText Anchor="badge#badge-style" TextStyle="TextStyle.H5" TagName="TagName.H2" class="rz-pt-12">
    Badge Style
</ElliciumText>
<ElliciumText TextStyle="TextStyle.Body1" class="rz-mb-8">
    To set a predefined badge style, use the <code>BadgeStyle</code> property, e.g. <code>BadgeStyle="BadgeStyle.Primary"</code>.
</ElliciumText>
<ElliciumExample ComponentName="Badge" Example="BadgeStyles">
    <BadgeStyles />
</ElliciumExample>

<ElliciumText Anchor="badge#badge-shade" TextStyle="TextStyle.H5" TagName="TagName.H2" class="rz-pt-12">
    Badge Shade
</ElliciumText>
<ElliciumText TextStyle="TextStyle.Body1" class="rz-mb-8">
    Each badge style, except Light and Dark, comes with a set of shades. Use the <code>Shade</code> property, e.g. <code>Shade="Shade.Lighter"</code>.
</ElliciumText>
<ElliciumExample ComponentName="Badge" Example="BadgeShades">
    <BadgeShades />
</ElliciumExample>

<ElliciumText Anchor="badge#badge-variant" TextStyle="TextStyle.H5" TagName="TagName.H2" class="rz-pt-12">
    Badge Variant
</ElliciumText>
<ElliciumText TextStyle="TextStyle.Body1" class="rz-mb-8">
    Each badge style and shade can be used with different badge variants. Use the <code>Variant</code> property, e.g. <code>Variant="Variant.Outlined"</code>.
</ElliciumText>
<ElliciumExample ComponentName="Badge" Example="BadgeVariants">
    <BadgeVariants />
</ElliciumExample>

<ElliciumText Anchor="badge#pill" TextStyle="TextStyle.H5" TagName="TagName.H2" class="rz-pt-12">
    Pill
</ElliciumText>
<ElliciumText TextStyle="TextStyle.Body1" class="rz-mb-8">
    Use <code>IsPill="true"</code> for pill-shaped badges.
</ElliciumText>
<ElliciumExample ComponentName="Badge" Example="BadgePills">
    <BadgePills />
</ElliciumExample>

